description: This skill helps you find out whether you should put fruits or vegetables in the refrigerator or in the pantry.  For example, you can ask Fruit Stand, "How do I store bananas?"
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Fruit Stand, how do I store parsley?
Alexa, ask Fruit Stand, how do I store these bananas?
Alexa, ask Fruit Stand, how do I store cucumbers?
name: Fruit Stand
shortDescription: Helps you store fruits and vegetables in the right place
